# Netflix Blocklist for Pi-hole
# ============================
# This list blocks the main domains used by Netflix for streaming, apps, and the website.
# Add this list to your Pi-hole Adlists section to block Netflix on all devices.
#
# Maintained by: [Greg]
# Last updated: 2025-05-25
#
# -- Main Netflix domains --
netflix.com
www.netflix.com
netflix.net
www.netflix.net

# -- Netflix streaming and API domains --
nflximg.com
www.nflximg.com
nflximg.net
www.nflximg.net
nflxso.net
www.nflxso.net
nflxvideo.net
www.nflxvideo.net
nflxext.com
www.nflxext.com
nflxsearch.net
www.nflxsearch.net
nflxmulti.net
www.nflxmulti.net
nflxpl.com
www.nflxpl.com

# -- Netflix CDN and service endpoints --
api-global.netflix.com
api-www.netflix.com
ios.prod.ftl.netflix.com
android.prod.ftl.netflix.com
help.netflix.com
movies.netflix.com
secure.netflix.com
signup.netflix.com
assets.nflxext.com
cds-api.netflix.com

# -- Netflix telemetry and tracking --
ichnaea.netflix.com
logging.netflix.com
metrics.netflix.com

# End of list
